						               													<description>Collect Kritters with splotches in three primary colours Cyan, Magenta and Yellow, and get hold of mixing bowls and paintbrushes to fill them with life. Use magic wands to change colours as needed to buy more Kritters, and add to your collection with bonus Kritters in secondary colours Red, Blue and Green.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Colour MY Kritters is a classic deck builder card game designed for younger players. You start with a few cards, and every round you have the chance to buy another card from the table. Cards have colour splotches (in three different primary colours, plus a wild card &amp;quot;colour&amp;quot;), and you use these to buy new cards. In the end you score the number of cards in each colour, but only for the colors you can supplement with a mixing bowl and/or a paintbrush. In addition comes bonus points on cards with Kritters in secondary colours.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Tabletopia: Play Colour MY Kritters for free on Tabletopia - you can try the game yourself and see how you like it :-) Find it there or on the official website (link below).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Print-and-play: A free PnP file can be downloaded from the official website (link below).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Kickstarter: A campaign for the printed edition of Colour MY Kritters was successfully funded on Kickstarter in December 2020 (link below). Late pledges will soon open so you can get your own copy even if you missed the Kickstarter.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
